  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_857bfe61d78102431a43f3356120f7d3">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Composite photographs and prints of the students and faculty members who attended the winter short courses at Cornell. Composites include the general agriculture, poultry, dairy, and horticulture classes, 1907-1926.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_5907c7c3c667c79034cf5faaff8800c1">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Also, 36 directories of students and announcements of courses, 1903-1943.</p>  </scopecontent>
